The paper discusses the development of a library for representing three-dimensional molecules using multidimensional arrays, which is designed for seamless integration with popular deep learning frameworks and leverages GPUs for computationally-intensive tasks. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG), Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE), and Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science (cs.CE) sub-categories.
